actions.text: Referred to the Committee on Foreign Affairs, and in addition to the Committees on Financial Services, the Judiciary, Ways and Means, and Oversight and Government Reform, for a period to be subsequently determined by the Speaker, in each case for consideration of such provisions as fall within the jurisdiction of the committee concerned.
Referred to House Ways and Means
Referred to House Oversight and Government Reform
Referred to the Subcommittee on Trade.
Ordered to be Reported in the Nature of a Substitute (Amended) by Voice Vote.
